  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>So, you're inside the psychological trauma of Rosaline. Help her achieve inner peace</strong>!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Learn her story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By listening to Rosaline's story, find a way to heal her childhood traumas as her psychotherapist</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/a548a3cddf062f83135581566b956205.poster.avif?t=1741291350\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/a548a3cddf062f83135581566b956205.webm?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/a548a3cddf062f83135581566b956205.mp4?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight with demons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat her inner demons that keep her mind imprisoned like a jail. Use the AK, revolver, shotgun, and other weapons, or rely on puzzle-solving and quest-passing skills to achieve this</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/f308b575c5e4de01968fd8640ce5b706.poster.avif?t=1741291350\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/f308b575c5e4de01968fd8640ce5b706.webm?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/f308b575c5e4de01968fd8640ce5b706.mp4?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Help her find inner peace and show it to her</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/7d3f38a1629e0f7fda3f00c3bc59ca82.poster.avif?t=1741291350\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/7d3f38a1629e0f7fda3f00c3bc59ca82.webm?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/7d3f38a1629e0f7fda3f00c3bc59ca82.mp4?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>So, you're inside the psychological trauma of Rosaline. Help her achieve inner peace</strong>!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Learn her story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By listening to Rosaline's story, find a way to heal her childhood traumas as her psychotherapist</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/a548a3cddf062f83135581566b956205.poster.avif?t=1741291350\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/a548a3cddf062f83135581566b956205.webm?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/a548a3cddf062f83135581566b956205.mp4?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fight with demons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat her inner demons that keep her mind imprisoned like a jail. Use the AK, revolver, shotgun, and other weapons, or rely on puzzle-solving and quest-passing skills to achieve this</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/f308b575c5e4de01968fd8640ce5b706.poster.avif?t=1741291350\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/f308b575c5e4de01968fd8640ce5b706.webm?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888200/extras/f308b575c5e4de01968fd8640ce5b706.mp4?t=1741291350\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >